src_text: Depeeletso Kabinete e amogetse peeletso ya R3 bilione e e dirilweng ke Setlamo sa Ford Motor mo Polanteng ya kwa Silverton, Pretoria, Gauten Peeletso eno e tla tlhola ditiro tse di maleba le tse di seng maleba go lebilwe tlhagiso e e tla oketsegang ya sejanaga sa yona sa mobetlo wa Ford Range Dipeeletso tsa mothale o di bontsha tiro eo re tsweletseng go samagana nayo jaaka puso mo go godiseng ikonomi le go samagana le dikgwetlho tsa botlhokatir Ka sekema sa puso mo Lenaaneng la Tlhagiso le Tlhabololo ya Dijanaga sa bokanaka Rbilione,go buletswe dipeeletso tsa ditlamo tsa poraefete tsa bokanaka R2bilione Tseno di akaretsa ditsiboso tse di dirilweng ke Toyota tsa maikaelelo a yona a go tlhagisa dijanaga tsa yona tsa mebetlo ya Toyota Hilux le Fortuner Paka ya Lekgetho ya 2017 Kabinete e leboga baduelalekgetho botlhe bao ba setseng ba dirile dipusetso tsa lekgetho tsa ngwaga wa lekgetho wa 2016/12.

src_text: Madikokoanyo ao a kokoangwang go tswa mo lekgethong la megolo a kgontsha puso go nna le bokgoni jwa go tlamela ka ditirelo tse di tlhokagalang thata mmogo le go tshegetsa maAforika Borwa a a dikobo dikhutshwan Kabinete e gopotsa baduelalekgetho gore letlha la bofelo la go dira dipusetso tsa lekgetho ke Labotlhano la bo 24 Ngwanaitseele 2017 mme e ba rotloetsa go di tlisa go sa le gale Kamogelo ya Khonferense ya Naga ya Tlhabololo ya Ikonomi ya Selegae (LED) Kabinete e itumedisitswe ke dipoelo tsa Khonferense ya Boset haba ya LED e e neng e tshwerwe mo maloben E ne e tshwerwe go latela boeteledipele jwa Tona ya Lefapha la Pusotshwaraganelo le Merero ya Setso (COGTA), Rre Des van Rooyen mmogo le Tona ya Lefapha la Tlhabololo ya Dikgwebopotlana, Mme Lindiwe Zul E abelane ka t hono ya go tlhagisa mogopolo o mont hwa wa LED ya Aforika Borwa o o supetswang tsela ke ditlapele tsa Leano la Tlhabololo la Boset haba (NDP).

src_text: Kabinete e batla go netefaletsa baagi gore puso ya naga, ya porofense le ya selegae e dirisana mmogo go netefatsa gore Aforika Borwa ga e kgale mets Kabinete e rotloetsa batho botlhe go nna le karolo mo go somareleng le mo go a diriseng ka go se a senye metsi Zimbabwe Kabinete e tshegetsa kgato ya tsereganyo e e tserweng ke Moporesitente Jacob Zuma, mo maemong a gagwe jaaka Monnasetulo wa Dinaga tsa Mokgatlho wa Tlhabololo ya Borwa jwa Aforika (SADC) mo go tsibogeleng seemo sa kwa Zimbabw O rometse Baromiwa ba Sesole ba ba Itlhophileng, Tona ya Sesole sa Tshireletso ya Naga le Bagale ba Sesole, Mme Nosiviwe Mapisa-Nqakula mmogo le Tona ya Pabalesego ya Puso ya Naga, Moatefokate Bongani Bong Ba tla kopana le Moporesitente Robert Mugabe mmogo le Sesole sa Tshireletso ya Naga ya Zimbabw Ka jalo, ba tla tsibosa Moporesitente wa Angola Jo o Louren o mo maemong a gagwe jaaka Monnasetulo wa SADC mo Lekaleng la Sepolotiki, Sesole le Pabaleseg Kantoro ya Moporesitente e tla abelana ka tshedimosetso e nngwe mo ntlheng eno fa nako e ntse e tsamaya

src_text: Ditsibosopeonakong ka ga letsholo la go tsenya diaterese le go neelana ka diaterese Kabinete e tsopoletswe ka ga pegelo ya kgatelopele mo go tsenyeng tirisong Katlholo ya Kgotlatshekelo ya Molaotheo ya go tsenya diaterese mo lenaaneng la batlhoph Kabinete e leboga kobamelo ka botlalo ya pegelo ya kgatelopele ya dikgwedi di le thataro e e rometsweng kwa Kgotlatshekelo ya Molaothe Go fitlha ga jaanong khomi ene ya Ditlhopho e e Ikemetseng (IEC), ka go dirisana mmogo le ditheo tse dingwe tsa puso, e fitlheletse katlego e e kanaka 75% mo go bokeletseng diaterese tsa batho bao ba batlang go ka tsenela ditlhoph Kabinete gape e ne ya nopolelwa ka ga lenaane le le rulagantsweng ke ba Ditireloposo tsa Aforika Borwa (SAPO) go ka thusa bao ba senang diaterese mo metseng ya bon Kabinete e itumeletse kgatelopele e e setseng e dirilwe go fitlha ga jaana mmogo le tirisanommogo magareng ga SAPO, IEC le ditheo tse dingwe tsa puso mo tirong eno ya porojekeng ya diateres Kabinete gape e ikuela mo go bao ba iseng ba tsenyedinakong diaterese tsa bona gore ba dire jalo mo bekeng e e latelang ya ikwadisetso ditlhopho ka Mopitlwe 2018.

src_text: Naga ya Aforika Borwa le ya Botswana di kopana ngwaga o mongwe le o mongwe mo maemong a go nna Ditlhogo tsa Dinaga mo letlhomesong la BNC go leba se wa botsalano jwa bonagapedi mmogo le go buisanela merero e e amang dinaga ka bobediDinaga ka bobedi di na le botsalano jo bo tseneletseng jo bo tlhodilweng ke kamano ya ditso tsa tsone le go nna baagisani ba ba gauf Di dirisana mo mererong e le mentsi e e akaretsang dipalangwa, kgwebisano le dipeeletso, boitekanelo, merero ya tikologo mmogo le merero e mengwe gape e mentsintsi Aforika Borwa ke mogwebisani yo mongwe wa bagwebisani ba bagolo ba Botswana, ka ditlamo di le mmalwa tsa yone tse ga jaanong di direlang kwa nageng e Leeto la Semmuso la Moporesitente wa Puso ya Angola1 Moporesitente Zuma o tla amogela Motlotlegi, Moporesitente wa Rephaboliki ya Angola, Jo o Louren o, mo Leeto la Semmuso le le tla dirang hisetori mo nageng ya Aforika Borwa go simolola ka la bo 23 Ngwanaitseele 2017.
trg_text: historical and fraternal ties dating back from the days of the liberation struggle when Angola housed and supported South African liberation cadres in various camps in that countryTrade and economic cooperation between the two countries has grown substantially, to the extent that South Africa is Angola s number one trading partner on the continen Many South African companies are conducting business in Angola in a variety of sectors including construction, mining, housing, retail, food and beverages, hotels and leisure, banking and medical serviceDuring his visit Jo o Louren o will also host a Lecture on 24 November 2017 at OR Tambo Building in Pretori 16 Days of Activism1 Cabinet joins all South Africans who are taking a stand against women and child abuseThe 16 Days of Activism for No Violence against Women and Children campaign is taking place between 25 November and 10 December 2017.

src_text: Kabinete e akgotse Fora go bo e le naga e e atlenegisitsweng go ka tshwarela kwa go yona Sejana sa Lefatshe tsa Rakabi sa 2023 mme e leboga boemedi jwa puso, jo bo neng bo eteletswe pele ke Motlatsamoporesitente Cyril Ramaphosa, Tona ya Metshameko le Boitapoloso Thulas Nxesi mmogo le Mokgatlhotshwaraganelo wa Aforika Borwa wa Rakabi, ka tiro e e dirilweng mo go tsholetseng maiteko a Aforika Borwa a go ka tshwarela meletlo eo kwan Kabinete e akgotse Tona Pandor, yo a abetsweng Kabo ya Morutabaithuti yo o Diphats Kabo eno e neetswe Tona Pandor, ke Molaodi wa Yunibesiti ya Aforika Borwa, Moporesitente wa mo malobeng rre Thabo MbekKabo ya Morutabaithuti yo o Diphatsa, e leng e nngwe ya dikabo di le nne, e leboga seabe sa barutabaithuti ba ba diphatsa ba ba dirileng bontle mo thutong le mo go godiseng thuto, go ithuta, tlhabololo ya bokgoni le/dipatlisiso mo dikarolong tse ba di itseng jaaka ba ikits Kabinete e akgotse tiro e e dirilweng ke Lefelopatlisiso la Boithutelalefaufau la Aforika Borwa, e leng karolo ya Diphuruphutso tsa Dipatlisiso ka Bophara tsa batsomi ba molokoloko wa Dipholanete bao ba boneng dipholanete tse dingwe tse dint hwa di le thar Kabinete e akgotse batsayakarolo le bafenyi ba Dikabo tsa 2017 tsa Govan Mbeki, tseo di bontshang tlotlo mo go bao ba leng mo lekaleng la kago leo le dirileng bontle mo go ageng dintl Dikabo tseno di tla mo nakong eo puso e tsweletseng go keteka kabelo ya dintlo le madulo a puso e thusang ka tlamelo ya matlole mo go one a feta milione fa e sale ka 199.
